== Importing ==

From file, import pokemon_number, level, ivs, evs, nature and moves
                             pokemon_number  =>  base_stats, type
  base_stats, level, ivs, evs, nature, type  =>  stats


Player info:
  Name, (remaining) team



== Battle ==

Player inputs:
  Use move    ->  Which move?
  Switch out  ->  Which Pokemon?


Damage calculation:
  Action priority: Switching > Move priority > Pokemon speed > Random
  If a pokemon dies, player must switch out
    If not attacked yet, attack is cancelled
    If can't switch out, then lose game
